Math.description: Mathematical operations, arithmetic, and numeric functions

functions.name: abs
functions.description: Return absolute value of a number
parameters: number: The input number (positive or negative)
functions.returns: Absolute value of the input number (always non-negative)

functions.name: avg
functions.description: Calculate average of numeric array elements

functions.name: ceil
functions.description: Round number up to next integer

functions.name: floor
functions.description: Round number down to previous integer

functions.name: max
functions.description: Find maximum value in numeric array

functions.name: min
functions.description: Find minimum value in numeric array

functions.name: round
parameters: number: The input number to round
functions.returns: Number rounded to nearest integer (.5 rounds up)

functions.name: sum
functions.description: Calculate sum of numeric array elements

Encoding.description: Base64, URL encoding/decoding, and cryptographic hashing

functions.description: URL encode string for web safety

XML.description: XML parsing, encoding detection, and namespace handling

String.description: Text processing, case conversion, and string manipulation

Array.description: Functional operations, filtering, mapping, and array manipulation

functions.name: every
functions.description: Check if all elements match a condition

functions.name: filter
functions.description: Filter array elements that match a condition

functions.name: find
functions.description: Find first element matching a condition

functions.name: findIndex
functions.description: Find index of first element matching condition
parameters: array: The input array to search
predicate: Function that tests each element (element) => boolean
functions.returns: Index of first matching element, or null if none found
functions.performance: O(n) time complexity, stops at first match

functions.name: map
functions.description: Transform each element of an array using a function

functions.name: reduce
functions.description: Reduce array to single value using accumulator function

functions.name: some
functions.description: Check if any element matches a condition
